dct_title_s: Bourdelois, pays de Medoc, et la prevoste de Born.; Bovrdelois, pays de Medoc, et la prevoste de Born.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. North oriented to the leftof the map. Includes a decorative cartouche with grapes and vines, compass rose, and illustrations of ships on the ocean. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 38 x 49 cm.
